A. Files

A-1  Create a file called "dont", and change something so that you cannot  delete it by running:
        rm dont
     Now, change back and delete the file

A-2  Create a directory called "mylog" and mount "/var/log" in it.
     undo

A-3  Copy ls into your home directory, and rename to "myls"
     Create a hard link to it called hardls (and demonstrate using it)
     remove myls, then try to use the hard link
     -------------------------------------------

A-4  Copy ls into your home directory, and rename to "myls"
     create a soft link to it called softls  (demonstrate using it)
     remove myls, then try to use the soft link
